OL,3,CHealth secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,CPIP disability benefits U-turn
OL,6,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,7,FKendall is expected to announce
OL,8,Freforms on Tuesday aimed at cutting a
OL,9,Fwelfare bill that ministers have
OL,10,Fdescribed as "unsustainable".
OL,12,FAhead of the announcement, speculation
OL,13,Fhas mounted that PIP ` the main
OL,14,Fbenefit for working-age adults ` could
OL,15,Fbe frozen rather than increased in
OL,16,Fline with inflation, delivering a real-
OL,17,Fterms cut for 3.6 million claimants.
OL,19,FBut on Sunday, reports suggested the
OL,20,Fgovernment is considering reversing
OL,21,Fcourse on PIP.
