OL,3,CHealth secretary refuses to rule out
OL,4,CPIP disability benefits U-turn
OL,6,FAsked about the speculation on Sunday,
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said he
OL,8,Fhas not yet seen the full proposals
OL,9,Fbut is sure Ms Kendall "wants to
OL,10,Fsupport people who need help the most"
OL,11,Fand will "make sure that there is a
OL,12,Fwide range of support".
OL,14,FHe told the BBC's Sunday With Laura
OL,15,FKuenssberg: "I haven't seen the
OL,16,Fproposals but you've seen the
OL,17,Fbriefing, you've seen the speculation,
OL,18,FI think the moral of the story is wait
OL,19,Ffor the plans."
