OL,6,FDuring his interview, Mr Streeting
OL,7,Falso said he believes there is an
OL,8,F"overdiagnosis" of mental health
OL,9,Fconditions leading to "too many people
OL,10,Fbeing written off" as unable to work.
OL,12,FCampaigners have urged the government
OL,13,Fnot to cut PIP, saying it would only
OL,14,Fserve to push disabled people into
OL,15,Fpoverty.
OL,17,FA PIP recipient with multiple
OL,18,Fsclerosis told the MS Society the
OL,19,Fprospect of cuts "scares the hell out
OL,20,Fof me".
