OL,6,FThey added: "Even with my husband's
OL,7,Fincome and my PIP payments, our
OL,8,Ffinances just disappear each month.
OL,10,F"My MS means I have extra costs like
OL,11,Ftaking supplements and accessing
OL,12,Fdifferent therapies which can be
OL,13,Fexpensive. Alongside that, our day-to-
OL,14,Fday living costs are increasing."
OL,16,FAttacks on the government have also
OL,17,Fcome from opposition parties, with the
OL,18,FSNP's Kirsty Blackman calling for the
OL,19,FPM to "apologise" to disabled people
OL,20,Ffor "allowing damaging speculation to
OL,21,Frun wild".
