OL,6,FMs Kendall is expected to attempt to
OL,7,Freassure people receiving disability
OL,8,Fbenefits by introducing a "right to
OL,9,Ftry guarantee" that will allow them to
OL,10,Ftake up work without necessarily
OL,11,Flosing their entitlements.
OL,13,FThe move is said to be in response to
OL,14,Fsurveys suggesting disabled people and
OL,15,Fthose with long-term health conditions
OL,16,Ffear they will not get their benefits
OL,17,Fback if they try employment but it
OL,18,Fdoes not work out.
